    • Constructor Detail

      • TGSuggestRequest

        public TGSuggestRequest(java.lang.String searchString,
                        com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.geometry.LatLng location)
        Create a suggest request with the required and optional parameters.
        Parameters:
        searchString - The input text entered by a user which is used by the suggest operation to generate a list of possible matches.
        location - Defines an origin point location to improve the search results. Possible values include the user's current location, or the center point of their current view.
